I bought a gift and I think it went well because he gave it not told me otherwise.

I ordered this product and immediately received verification the next day showing that the sender had done their part to ship it.  After the product came in, I opened a few of the dvd's and noticed several scratches on some of them.  It appeared that a few of the dvd's were damaged and unwatchable, so I contacted the seller through email and received a quick response apologizing for my inconvenience and they immediately refunded my money w/o a dispute.  Although the product wasn't exactly what I was hoping for, the seller was very friendly and accommodating.

I was not really sure if I would be into this show but my wife got them for me and I have to say after two epesiodes I was hooked and it made it so nice to have all the seasons together so I did not have to wait for the next one to get here when I finished one great deal.
This product got to me very fast and all the items were in perfect condition. I am very happy with it and would do it again in a heartbeat!
gave to my husband for gift, opened first season to watch and disc so scratched we cant watch,,will not buy from amazon again
I received the entorauge dvds 2 1/2 weeks after ordered... took a little long, but the quality of the product has been great!  Will order from this company again.

I was disappointed with this purchase. When watching the dvd you will notice that the subtitles are always on and you'll have to turn them off manually at the start of each viewing. Also some parts were blacked out or distorted with pixles to cover up any or all nudity from the show, something which is uncensored here on the US show. The Seller should have stated that some of the seasons are not from the US HBO show and censored for other markets. With that being said purchase at your own risk.....
